Class AnimatedCube

java.lang.Object
  hyperbolize.animation.Animation
      hyperbolize.animation.AnimatedCube
All Implemented Interfaces:
Objet
public class AnimatedCube
extends Animation
implements Objet

This class extends the animation scheme for cubes. Given a starting cube and an ending cube with respective coordinates and colors, it allows an animated cube to be drawn by interpolation.
